AdvRS = {import:adv-random-styles}
betterSEQUENCE = {import:better-sequencer}

Time
  // Daytime:
  Early Morning
    the dawn breaking, soft sunlight filtering through, morning mist hovering over the ground
  Mid-Morning
    a bright sunlight, long shadows cast, the freshness of the day in full bloom
  Noon
    the blazing sun is high in the sky, vibrant, intense daylight
  Afternoon
    it's the golden hour light, gentle warmth, sunlight casting soft, long shadows
  Evening
    the dusk setting in, cool air rising, soft glow of the setting sun, horizon painted in warm hues

  // Nighttime
  Twilight
    a fading sunlight, sky glowing in deep purples and blues, the first stars appearing
  Early Night
    the dark sky is settling in, the moon rising, crisp and cool night air, a scattering of stars
  Midnight
    it's deep, dark night, the sky fully blanketed in stars, {the moon shining bright|the moon hidden behind clouds}
  Late Night
    it's quiet, stillness, faint glows of distant lights, the world at rest, only the sound of the night breeze
  Pre-Dawn
    it's dark, silent, the faintest hint of light at the horizon, the night preparing to give way to day
SpecialTime
  Purple Dawn (Special)
    a still, darkened sky, dark dawn, indigo and violet hues linger, peace and silence
  Red Sunset (Special)
    the sunset casting red light, an intense exposed red sky, oversaturated, sky in crimson shades, deep vibrant, dimlit in crimson
  Horror Time (Special)
    a shadowed twilight, where the surroundings twist under dim violet skies, fog creeping close to the ground, obscuring unseen paths
Season
  Spring I
    vibrant blooms bursting through fresh green growth, alive with gentle warmth and light fragrances
  Spring II
    soft petals blanket the earth, gentle breezes scatter new leaves across delicate buds
  Summer I
    rich, golden fields, buzzing with vibrant energy and warm winds, dense foliage all around
  Summer II
    the air feels thick with the scent of flowers, everything alive with intense colors
  Autumn I
    fiery leaves drift through crisp, refreshing air, trees cloaked in warm hues and fallen foliage
  Autumn II
    earthy scents rise from the ground, leaves falling in amber and crimson cascades
  Winter I
    glittering frost covers every surface, branches heavy with snow, an untouched, quiet landscape
  Winter II
    dense, cold mist hangs in the air, surroundings blanketed in serene, crystal-coated silence
  Monsoon I
    clouds pour over lush, dense greenery, wet earth and rivers swelling under constant rainfall
  Monsoon II
    heavy rains and saturated surroundings, a lush landscape under dark clouds, filled with moisture and vitality
  Drought I
    cracked earth stretches across a dry, arid landscape, sparse vegetation wilting under intense heat
  Drought II
    barren, cracked terrain with dry air, sparse growth and a sense of lingering heat, resilient under the relentless dryness
  Early Frost I
    unseasonal frost cloaks trees, a delicate layer of ice on leaves and stems, fields covered in silvery sheen
  Early Frost II
    a sudden chill grips the scene, fine crystals of frost coating surfaces, signaling the onset of a colder phase
  Mist-Laden Season I
    heavy mist clings low to the ground, obscuring distant trees, creating a dreamlike, softened atmosphere
  Mist-Laden Season II
    soft mist veils the view, a gentle haze settling in, lending an ethereal feel to the surroundings

Rains
  Drizzle
    Light, misty droplets that softly blanket surroundings, often filling the air with a fine haze
  Mountain Showers
    Sudden, short bursts of rain often moving swiftly over mountain slopes, accompanied by bursts of fog and cool breezes
  Monsoon Downpour
    Intense, relentless rain with large, heavy drops that saturate the ground rapidly
  Freezing Rain
    hailstones falling covering the ground in a thick layer, coating surfaces in a slippery, glassy layer
  Tropical Rainstorm
    A warm, heavy rain with large drops, often occurring in tropical rainforests, lush and brief but powerful.
  Foggy Drizzle
    A slow, near-silent drizzle that mingles with fog, creating an eerie stillness
  Thunderstorm Rain
    Fierce, pounding rain accompanied by thunder, lightning, and occasional gusts
  Urban Summer Shower
    A sudden, warm rain with the distinct smell of pavement

