  Burned (special) 🔸
    [BGSCENE] a scenery where charred husks of trees dominate the horizon, their warped shapes rising against a stark, desolate backdrop. The earth is hardened and dry, littered with fragments of burned and splintered timber[SceneNgtv('fire:0.7')]
  Decaying Forest (special) 🔸
    [BGSCENE] a sceenry where trees stand lifeless, their bark cracked and weathered, trunks with no leaves, their gnarled branches clawing at the empty expanse. The ground is blanketed with ashen debris, dry bark and splintered wood scattered across the barren soil, the forest is steeped in decay[SceneNgtv('greenery:0.7')]

  Mystic Forest (special) 🔸
    [BGSCENE] a mystical forest, trees, plants, and mushrooms are intense glowing in spectrum of vibrant colors. Trunks shimmer with blues and purples, leaves pulse with pinks and yellows. The floor is bathed in a colorful light from bioluminescent flora, each element radiating an intense glow that blends and spreads, creating a magical, ever-changing atmosphere of illumination and enchantment

  Red Forest (special) 🔸
    [BGSCENE] a mysterious peaceful forest where deep black trunks and branches stretch out like silhouettes against a rich, dark red sky. The leaves and undergrowth are tinged with shades of crimson, casting a warm, subdued glow throughout the landscape. The ground is soft with dark soil, dotted with red flowers. The forest exudes a calm atmosphere

  White Frozen Forest (special) 🔸
    [BGSCENE] a frozen forest where everything is encased in translucent ice, with branches and trunks shimmering like frosted glass. The ice captures the light, creating soft, reflective effects that mirror the surroundings, amplifying the stillness. The dominant white tones blend with the glistening reflections, creating an ethereal, crystalline landscape

Ruins
  Ancient City (Rock-cut Architecture)
    [BGSCENE] an ancient city carved into red sandstone cliffs, featuring the treasury and monumental rock-cut architecture

  Ancient City II
    [BGSCENE] an ancient city carved into rose-red cliffs, with intricate facades and narrow canyons

  Ancient Temple Ruins
    [BGSCENE] an ancient temple ruins covered in divine, glowing vines and flowers, massive stone pillars, devastated, etched with faded sacred symbols, crumble under the weight of time, but still radiate a faint golden light, the altar at the heart of the temple is destroyed and cracked, yet untouched by nature, surrounded by ethereal beams of sunlight filtering through the broken roof, soft white moss and luminescent plants create a tranquil aura

  Dark Jungle Ruins
    [BGSCENE] a shadowy jungle ruins where the lush greens are replaced with deep blues and purples, the towering trees have dark, navy bark, while their leaves glow softly in hues of indigo and violet, and exotic, bioluminescent flowers in shades of blue and lavender bloom from cracks in the ancient stone walls, the air is filled with a faint mist that reflects soft light, creating a dim but serene atmosphere, the ruins themselves are bathed in pale moonlight, casting a soft glow on the blue-tinted vines and stones, giving the landscape a mystical, peaceful aura

  Egypt
    The background is a scenery of fertile banks lined with ancient temples, tombs, and remnants of pharaonic history

  Egypt II
    [BGSCENE] an ancient temple, with towering pillars, statues, and hieroglyphics

  Unusual Frozen Ruins
    [INBG], frozen ruins where the icy surfaces shimmer with deep reds and crimson hues, the frost-covered stones reflect a warm, soft glow, as fiery red and orange lights flicker across the frozen structures, creating a striking contrast with the cold, thin layers of red-tinted ice catch the light, giving the entire scene a molten, yet frozen effect, snowflakes glisten in shades of scarlet and amber, casting faint sparkles that illuminate the ruins in a warm, yet eerie, ethereal light

Urban
  🎲 Urban (21)🔻
    [AdvRS("urbanScene", urbanbanlist = ["🎲 Urban (21)🔻"], Urban), urbanSceneRandomItem]

  Clean and Modern City
    [BGSCENE] a cityscape that embodies cleanliness and modernity, featuring translucent, minimalistic buildings with sleek, white facades and expansive glass surfaces //. Soft, ambient lighting creates a serene, calm atmosphere, with gently curved, unobtrusive structures blending seamlessly into the landscape. Streets are smooth and uncluttered, with subtle, elegant illumination and a restrained color palette of whites, grays, and soft pastels, contributing to a peaceful, uncluttered urban environment

  Cute City
    [BGSCENE] a dreamy and cheerful cityscape bursting with cute, kawaii, and girly elements, where buildings in pink, lavender, and mint green create a whimsical atmosphere; the architecture is decorated with cute details, puffy clouds and rainbow-like arches span across bridges, lamp posts resemble lollipops, and cute cafes with oversized desserts line the streets //a cityscape bursting with cute, kawaii, and girly elements, where pastel-colored buildings in pink, lavender, and mint green create a soft, whimsical atmosphere. Heart-shaped windows, bows, and floral patterns adorn the architecture, while puffy clouds and rainbow-like arches span across bridges. Lamp posts resemble lollipops, and cute cafes with oversized desserts line the streets. Everything is designed with a playful, adorable touch, from the curvy roads to the bubbly fountains, creating a dreamy and cheerful urban environment

  Devasted City
    [BGSCENE] a grounded cityscape perspective with jagged, angular buildings with dark, harsh colors, deep reds, blacks, and steel grays, crumbling structures and sharp, spiked elements dominate the skyline, chaotic, fragmented pathways create a sense of unease and danger in the city

  Elegant and  Natural
    [BGSCENE] a cityscape blending modern and natural elements, where sleek, translucent buildings rise gracefully among lush greenery, elegant golden accents trim the structures, casting a soft, luxurious glow. The design features open, airy spaces with natural wood textures and flowing water integrated into the architecture; comfortable, cozy seating areas are woven into parks and plazas, pathways are lined with warm, subtle lighting, blending sophistication and nature in a harmonious, welcoming urban environment

  Medieval City
    [BGSCENE] a medieval city in a fantasy world where the architecture blends traditional elements with sleek, modern, curvy designs, towers and homes rise gracefully with sweeping arches and spiraling shapes, crafted from smooth, luminous materials that shimmer; the buildings feature a polished surfaces in vivid hues of blues, greens, and golds, with glowing, gem-like accents embedded in the walls, streets are wide and lined with elegant, curving pathways, illuminated by soft, magical light sources that give the city a bright, welcoming glow

  Neon City
    [BGSCENE] a modern cityscape bathed in colors like deep purples, rich magentas, and electric blues; glossy, reflective surfaces on sleek skyscrapers shimmer with vibrant, dynamic lighting, the ambient illumination create a seductive glow, while modern architecture enhances the city's sultry, high-fashion vibe; streets are lined with smooth, illuminated tiles that catch and reflect the city's colorful lights

